genresAdvancedInfo.name: wuhan indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Wuhan Indie is a genre of music that originated in the city of Wuhan, China. It is characterized by its DIY ethos and its rejection of mainstream pop music. Wuhan Indie artists often incorporate elements of traditional Chinese music and culture into their music, as well as influences from Western indie rock and punk. The genre gained international attention in 2020, when Wuhan became the epicenter of the COVID-19 pandemic.
